WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.600
I frequently say that god treats me better than I deserve. It is certainly

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:10.350
 true I've been happy with virtually every career ahead except for

00:00:10.350 --> 00:00:15.100
 practicing law. My time in the service were the best years of my

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:19.850
 life. The absolute best year in my life ever was my year in Vietnam

00:00:19.850 --> 00:00:24.600
 and my time and academia has just been a riot, I do enjoy it, pay has

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:29.350
 been decent, I've raised a family, educated three daughters and I

00:00:29.350 --> 00:00:34.100
 when I go to meet my maker I will be in full thanks for the life he

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:38.850
 has given me

